      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程画出来：idle到scanned的SCAN转换，scanned和viewing之间的SELECT/BACK往返，还有scanned自循环的SCAN。",
      "elements_involved": [
