      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加上EXPORT功能，scanned和viewing状态下都能导出数据。另外scanned状态要支持RESET回到idle，相当于清空当前会话。",
      "elements_involved": [
